  "original_title": "\u0daf\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba \u0db0\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dcf\u0dbb \u0dc3\u0dda\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dba\u0ddd \u0dba\u0dc5\u0dd2 \u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dca\u0da2\u0db1\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d85\u0dbb\u0db9\u0dad\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Railway station workers start a strike again",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Employees of several trade unions, including railway station employees, have started another strike and due to this, several trains have been canceled today (7) in the morning.",
        "Members of several railway unions are currently protesting for fuel by blocking the main entrance to the railway headquarters.",
        "Among the canceled trains is the inter-city express running from Colombo Fort to Kankasanthuraya at 11.50 am, the Railway Department said."
      ],
